      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "# Storage & Asset Serving\nFreeze (S3 upload), defrost (cold read-through), relay serving, DTSH generation, eviction, and sync-outcome reliability. Per-tenant/per-asset detail lives in Metabase (ClickHouse storage_events); this is cluster-wide ops.",
